        Returns:

      • contains

        boolean contains​(java.lang.String itemId,
                 double treshold)
        Checks if the bank contains an item with the specified ID and meets the threshold quantity.
        Parameters:
        itemId - The ID of the item to check.
        treshold - The minimum quantity threshold.
        Returns:
        true if the item exists in the bank in the specified quantity, false otherwise.

      • withdrawItem

        void withdrawItem​(java.lang.String itemId,
                  double treshold)
        Withdraws an item from the bank with the specified ID, if it meets the threshold quantity.
        Parameters:
        itemId - The ID of the item to withdraw.
        treshold - The minimum quantity threshold for withdrawal.
